'''愛琴海板塊'''是[[地中海|地中海]]東部的小型[[板塊|板塊]]，位於[[希臘|希臘]]南部和[[土耳其|土耳其]]西部，南面邊緣是[[克里特|克里特]]以南的[[隱沒帶|隱沒帶]]，南面的[[非洲板塊|非洲板塊]]沉入愛琴海板塊<ref>Meier, T ''et al.'' (2007) "A Model for the Hellenic Subduction Zone in the area of Crete based on seismological investigations" [http://books.google.com/books?id=rQ1mm4IzkAYC&pg=PA194 pp. 194-195] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=rQ1mm4IzkAYC&pg=PA194 |date=20141002161915 }} ''In'' Taymaz, Tuncay and Dilek, Yildirim (eds.) (2007) ''The Geodynamics of the Aegean and Anatolia'' Geological Society, London, pp. 183-200, ISBN 978-1-86239-239-7</ref>，而北面與[[歐亞大陸板塊|歐亞大陸板塊]]之間的[[分離板塊邊緣|分離板塊邊緣]]則形成[[科林斯灣|科林斯灣]]。

